  itemIcon: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 3114803160e2e5c48a249d0707d8db8f, type: 3}
  description: "Increases Critical Strike Chance by 20% and Health by 40. Grants
    \"Sanguine Desperation\": For every 10% of Maximum Health the wearer is missing,
    their Critical Strike Chance increases by 10%. Additionally, the wearer restores
    Health equal to 15% of all damage dealt to enemies. Coarse linen bandages that
    have long since lost their original color; they pulse with a dark, primal rhythm,
    turning the wearer's proximity to death into a surgeon\u2019s precision and a
    predator\u2019s thirst."
